  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Low, slow & unapologetically bold</p>
  <h1>Desi <em>Chicken</em><br>Curry</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Big bone-in pieces, rendered fat, tomato heat, green chili bite â€” the kind of curry that fills the whole kitchen with smell before it's halfway done.</p>
  <div class="hero-tags">
    <span class="tag">ğŸ— Serves 4â€“5</span>
    <span class="tag">ğŸ”¥ Spicy</span>
    <span class="tag">â± ~1.5 hrs</span>
    <span class="tag">ğŸ¦´ Bone-in</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="spice-strip">
  <span>ğŸŒ¶ Green chili</span>
  <span>ğŸ… Tomato</span>
  <span>ğŸ«š Whole spices</span>
